reviews.review_text: This Mc donalds on 56st in Delta/Tsawwassen had some of the best costumer service.  my friend Tyler and l and his son came in for breakfast, they got my order correct which usually never happens I order extra items, they gave reed a free ice cream and a colouring book. The lady working was extremely friendly and informed us when we sat in the childrens area that it hadnt been disinfected for three years and not to sit there. Yeah thumbs up great job

Very well run McDonald s. I always special order items and they are perfect. I order items  on the app. Mandeep knows all the regulars names and makes us feel welcome. Thank you ! Dietary restrictions: Special order

1835 56th Street McDonalds is great! I had a problem with an online order and Simran helped me and fixed everything. Thank you Simran! Service is great, the place is all clean, and people are working nicely and competently. Food

Great McDonalds.  Clean, fast service and nice store. Easily accessible on your way to the Ferry. Cool up front display of the baked goods etc.  Food was hot and right to order.  Bagel was so nice and fresh. Thanks!
Hands down best McDonald s. Service 10/10 , Speed 10/10 , Staff 10/10, Food- always hot & fresh 10/10. Ba da ba ba baaa I m lovin it Food

To all the ppl complaining about the workers and the orders 1. Most of em are just kids, and human, they make mistakes 2. Did you tell the whole story? You were probably extremely rude and confrontational, you get as much as you give. I find its exceptional service, even at 6 am, cheerful and bright. Have never screwed up my order. Keep up the good work!
Hey ThaNks for the lovely Treatment.Ashley
Clean, warm food served up fast, and pleasant service. One of the better ones.

People probably don t think to review a McDonalds but I just wanted to say that every time I come though, (the only drive through in town) I am greeted by the nicest, most polite employees. They must have a great leader as they all seem happy in their jobs. It s so nice to be greeted by people who are happy, friendly and personable.
Great service at this location. Online order took fast and quality was all right. Nice clean store.
The best McDonalds I ever visits. Staff are super friendly with high quality service. Never had any unpleasant experience.
Very clean and the food taste great. Fantastic play area for smaller kids.
Just drive thru, indecisive of our order, changed again, Overall smooth transaction Food
The fastest drive thru I have ever seen PIRIOD! GREAT WORK! Wheelchair accessibility: Its has it. Food : 4/5 |

Seriously, the friendliness McDonalds employees ever. I think they pulled all the super smiley happy people from fast food commercials and made them work here. Either that or management is pumping in some happy gas. Sure, they screw up now and again (not ever for me personally, but who doesnt)
Very nice location, always help out the community and have many friendly and helpful staff. They are very busy yet make less mistakes than other locations. :)
They are a good place for a McDonald , I had a coffee two cream was extremely good, their coffee are up there with Starbucks but their price so much better

Got my order wrong on size of fries. They exchanged no problem and kept the other size ad well. I am pleased with this kind of service. I wish all companies ran this good instead of making it to be a big deal to do their job.
Toby took our order in the drive through and was the best. Very pleasant and helpful. Food was Perf. Will be back.
Two ice creams to go. Nice people
Tsawwassens very own McDonalds has quick service at both the dining room and drive thru, and the dining room itself is cozy and clean.

As far as McDonalds go this location is great. Staff are all super friendly and when an order is wrong they are quick to fix it. Their drive thru is great - at least in my experience. No issues. The staff is often cleaning and tidying often so its clean (for the most part). We make use of the play space on occasion and its always clean when we go in. Grear customer service.

Charming...... I inadvertently forgot to ask for salt and pepper when I ordered our meal. Mr. Personality at the first window berated me and told me that he doesnt have to give me anything if I cant remember your ask for it when Im ordering the food. Rushing back??? Hmmmmm.... I think not.

Currently a fast food staple for me. Quick and fresh. Also covid restrictions arent that hindering. Just wear a mask while ordering, eat in the place and just put your mask back on after youre finished.
i love their morning staff. Always cheerful.

we had a very good experience at this location. Staff were very friendly and store looked very clean. lately we have used this fast food place at other locations and they have all been going down hill. This was a refreshing change to see food put together properly and placed neatly in a bag with a smiling face
Good drive through service!
We only ordered fries.

One of the nicest McD Ive visited in some time. An older (old) crowd who get together there on a daily/weekly basis. Really a nice, clean and decent atmosphere. Kudos to you guys for a fast food joint being so nice.

By far the best McDonalds around. Same owner as Ladner and they take pride in the cleanliness and service. Staff is friendly, helpful and the quality.of food is awesome. In the spring you will even see the owner doing gardening... I drive 20 minutes with the kids to come here.
really excellent service

I stopped in on the way to the ferry to get something for  the road. First visit. Had the best egg McMuffin ever. Fresh, smoking hot, juicy and with a huge piece of ham, as good as the ones we make from scratch at home. Coffee was delish too. While the happy pleasant, hardworking young ladies were  wearing their masks (covid), you could tell they were smiling underneath. This will now be my go to place for food for the ferry trip. Thanks!

The food here is so good, once in awhile there a couple mishaps, like a burnt patty or a missing item, but then again its fast food not a five star Gordon ramsay restaurant, wraps are always well made. Definitely suggest eating there
Tsawwassen location. Forgot how good pancakes were until I stopped in for a quick breakfast. Clean restaurant, good prices.
Nice place with nice staff.
Almost as Fast like they do in Japan. International McDonald s seam to remember its fast food for a reason. Fast!

Going through the drive-thru everyone was super friendly, much more than other McDonalds Ive been to. The drive-thru menu is one of those annoying electronic kinds that changes every few seconds though.
How do you rate McDonalds? I mean, you know what youre getting before you get it even before you decide. I never been surprised at McDs. And in a sense, thats a good thing.
These replies are funny y all acting like u never had McDonald s and it s a fancy restaurant or sum. Like I think most of us grew up with mcDs  bwt I m still a child but come on
Surprisingly good coffee. Fast cheerful service. Handicapped washrooms. Not a bad breakfast selection before 11 a.m. then it is egg mcm only.
Clean, friendly and fast. Has a drive thru, play area and now they have self serve ordering kiosks. One of the servers offered to throw our garbage away for us.
Very busy location. Always fast service both taking the order and getting the order into my hands. FYI the bathrooms are always spotless!
Not normally on my agenda but I wanted Fish and Chips yes with a twist  MacDonalds FF (CHIPS) and Salmon with a green salad.  EASY!!!
Our late night fast food run brought us here with 1 minute 29 seconds before closing time and they filled our order while remaining very friendly. Hats off to them !
My family loves Macdonald s! This one is as pleasant as any other ones.
Great fast food breaky.  Great coffee!
This is one of the better run McDonalds.  Manager is nice and polite, smiles.   Customer service oriented.  If only all McDonalds were like this one...
Good McDonalds location! Have had good experiences here. Have nothing bad to say. Quickly served and good food.
the food was very fresh and all the workers was wearing mask and gloves. Now they dont were masks.
To the drive thru manager that is on shift on Saturday afternoons, you rock!! Thank you so much for being so professional and kind
Hooooot fries second time in a row. Love.
Although its not considered a busy mcdonalds location, service was great and staff were friendly.
Great Treat for the family. Kid-friendliness: Always makes the lil guys feel special
I dont know why not to rate it 5 stars because I mean it is just a Macdonalds I mean it was pretty clean so I guess that counts.
Everyone was very friendly and it was very quick
Love the meal deal coupons and speedy service.   Very accommodating to customers.

McDonalds is a once a week place for my family .But I buy coffees on my way to work Save stickers for free coffee McDonalds all seem to close around 4 am for reboot or something Inconvenient for me as Im up at that time weekdays
The new renovation looks great and cleaned on a regular basis.
Loved my egg mcmuffin!!!
First McDonald s earned my five stars review.
I feel the service is fast and efficient and the staff is friendly.
Cone is my favorite. Always go there with my kids. Kid-friendliness: Kids play ground Recommended dishes Mcflurries and a Baby Ice Cream Cone
Been to many McDonalds, but this one is clean, food actually looks like the pictures and the icecream cone tastes different.
Fun for my 3year old Kid-friendliness: Very small play area for kids. Food : 5/5 |
Great service ashton took my order and lightened my day good job!
This is one of the cleanest McDonalds Ive  been in and the staffs attitude is pleasant.
One of the nicest Ive been to.
Awesome loved it A+++++++++++ the kids really know what theyre doing. Angus burger is too expensive, do something bout that.
Friendly staff... I usually go there in afternoon... Fast service and great staff
Nice restaurant. Service was quick and friendly
These guys are always on the ball. Even when its bright and early. God bless them.
Honestly my favourite McDonalds. Its got a great vibe and decent waiting time.
Always good and consistent. But dining area should be cleaner.
Very fresh food at this location.
Polite and quick staff. Good, fresh coffee!
I love this place coz the crew members and *managers* are very friendly and helpful.
Great food and fast drive-thru service!
The GEL was amazing and my food was out before I fully paid
Very clean and friendly branch. I forgot to order as a meal and got a sandwich instead. The supervisor offered fries and pop on the house.
Fast friendly service. Very polite.
Mmmmmm coffeeeeee! Get it here before you hit the ferry!
Its mcdees what can i say nothing is the same. You get 5 stars when you are in your own category.
Came in looking for Fortnite burger it was not there came out with yummy burger
Always good when you need some fast food
super friendly staff
Clean and friendly. Good washrooms and free Wi-Fi!
Nice and hot food
Great food,and not super expensive
Good
Cant say enough about the breakfast wraps, they are so tasty and filling!
Good old mcDs, nice decor for a fast food place
They prepared my cheeseburger just right
Great service, great food!
I go to play the Monopoly game . I also like the coffee
Such a great McDonalds with fantastic staff
nice place clean and great staff.
Very friendly service
